data.description: Exciting Real Estate Opportunity!   I am thrilled to present to you an incredible income-producing 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath duplex that is now on the market! This gem is perfect for savvy investors or those looking to embrace the true essence of dual living.   Unit A will captivate you with its stylish ceramic flooring throughout, emphasizing luxury and durability. The laminate plank flooring in both bedrooms adds a touch of elegance. You'll adore the fresh new kitchen countertops and cabinets that truly enhance the space. And guess what? Washer and dryer are included, making laundry day a breeze!   Unit B has its own charms! With all new laminate plank flooring and modern countertops, it exudes a fresh and inviting ambiance. Although the washer and dryer hookups are included (set not provided), you can easily set them up based on your own preference. Plus, the brand-new roof completed in September 2022 ensures durability and peace of mind.   Ready for the best part? Unit B has generated an impressive $11,000 in income over the past year! The potential here is vast! Rent out one side and enjoy the perks of living in the other, or rent both sides and experience the true benefits of passive income. Unit A can fetch anywhere between $750-$800 in rent, while Unit B holds the potential to be leased for $800-$850.   Don't miss this golden opportunity to turn dreams into reality! Schedule a visit today and witness the incredible potential of this duplex.   For more details contact Phillip Thomas at 443-254-7844 or email at pthomas@parksjonesrealty.com.
